Here's a simple HTML website that displays a random joke from a list of 4 jokes when a user clicks a button.

### ✅ Features:
- A button that the user can click.
- When clicked, it shows a random joke from a predefined list.

---

### 📄 `index.html`

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Random Joke Generator</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 100px;
        }
        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #joke {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
